OL,3,CWatchdog reverses ruling that Calvin
OL,4,CKlein poster 'objectified' FKA twigs
OL,6,FThe advertising watchdog has reversed
OL,7,Fits own ruling that a Calvin Klein
OL,8,Fposter presented British musician FKA
OL,9,Ftwigs as a "stereotypical sexual
OL,10,Fobject".
OL,12,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,13,F(ASA) said it had decided to revisit
OL,14,Fits original decision in January that
OL,15,Fthe poster was likely to cause serious
OL,16,Fharm or offence by objectifying FKA
OL,17,Ftwigs "out of concern that our
OL,18,Frationale for banning the ad was
OL,19,Fsubstantially flawed".
